{"word":"παραλαμβάνω","slug":"παραλαμβάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παραλαμβάνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λαμβάνω\">λαμβάνω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘receive to one’s side’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> aspect <b>take <a href='B:470 1:20'>Mt 1:20</a>; <a href='B:470 2:13'>2:13f</a>; <a href='B:500 14:3'>J 14:3</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> aspect <b>receive<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>α.</pp></b> in general <b><a href='B:550 1:9'>Gal 1:9</a>, <a href='B:550 1:12'>12</a>; <a href='B:570 4:9'>Phil 4:9</a>; <a href='B:580 2:6'>Col 2:6</a>; <a href='B:590 4:1'>1 Th 4:1</a>; <a href='B:600 3:6'>2 Th 3:6</a>; <a href='B:650 12:28'>Hb 12:28</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>β.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> connotation of hospitable treatment <b><a href='B:500 1:11'>J 1:11</a>; <a href='B:530 15:1'>1 Cor 15:1</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>γ.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> connotation of obligation undertaken <b><a href='B:580 4:17'>Col 4:17</a>.<p class=\"pp4\"/>—<pp>δ.</pp></b> of receipt for custody <b><a href='B:510 16:33'>Ac 16:33</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to go along’, <b>take <a href='B:470 4:5'>Mt 4:5</a>; <a href='B:470 12:45'>12:45</a>; <a href='B:470 24:40'>24:40f</a>; <a href='B:470 27:27'>27:27</a>; <a href='B:480 10:32'>Mk 10:32</a>; <a href='B:490 9:28'>Lk 9:28</a>; <a href='B:510 15:39'>Ac 15:39</a>; <a href='B:510 21:24'>21:24</a>; <a href='B:510 23:18'>23:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παράλαβε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παραλέγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}